| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7432 — Recovery Inhibition (clop)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8f8303c4-4f75-52e2-b3f3-83fe45a27c2f"
